{"id":128,"date":"2021-09-29T04:48:19","date_gmt":"2021-09-29T04:48:19","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/?p=128"},"modified":"2021-11-07T16:26:31","modified_gmt":"2021-11-07T09:26:31","slug":"xxiipatch-card-do-hoa-nvidia","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/2021\/09\/29\/xxiipatch-card-do-hoa-nvidia\/","title":{"rendered":"XXII. Patch card \u0111\u1ed3 h\u1ecda NVIDIA"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>H\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c card \u0111\u1ed3 h\u1ecda nvidia \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 support \u1edf high sierra th\u00f4i c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 xem danh s\u00e1ch card h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 big sur <a href=\"https:\/\/heavietnam.ga\/phan-cung-phu-hop\/\">t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y<\/a> c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng card kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng card \u1edf high sierra th\u00f4i quy tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n l\u00e0m theo sau<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B1: M\u1edf terminal v\u00e0 g\u00f5&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>bash &lt;(curl -s <a href=\"https:\/\/raw.githubusercontent.com\/Benjamin-Dobell\/nvidia-update\/master\/nvidia-update.sh\">https:\/\/raw.githubusercontent.com\/Benjamin-Dobell\/nvidia-update\/master\/nvidia-update.sh<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B2: Th\u00eam code sau boot-arg nvda-drv=1&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>L\u01b0u \u00fd: Main source <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/nhat.dev\/hackintosh\/cai-web-driver-cho-card-roi-nvidia.html\"><strong>C\u00e0i Web Driver cho card r\u1eddi NVIDIA &#8211; nhat.dev<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>L\u01b0u \u00fd 2: \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng card nvidia h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 vram c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n th\u00eam boot-arg sau v\u00e0o : agdpmod=vit9696 ho\u1eb7c agdpmod=pikera<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>L\u01b0u \u00fd 3: \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n dgpu kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u1eefng v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n c\u00e0i l\u00ean big sur m\u00e0 l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m m\u00e0u cho dgpu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ee7 vram th\u00ec l\u00e0m theo sau ( c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap t\u0103ng vram kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap nh\u1eadn qe\/ci hay t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u n\u0103ng )<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>B1: <\/strong>G\u00f5 l\u1ec7nh sau v\u00e0o terminal&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>sudo nano \/System\/Library\/CoreServices\/SystemVersion.plist<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>B2: <\/strong>T\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee5c ProductBuildVersion v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5i m\u00e3 d\u1ef1ng v\u1ec1 high sierra l\u00e0 \u201c17G14042\u201d<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>B3: <\/strong>C\u00e0i nh\u01b0 h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn \u1edf tr\u00ean<strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>B4: <\/strong>Restart v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng<strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>L\u01b0u \u00fd 4: C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e0i 1 s\u1ed1 app kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00ean macos big sur (nh\u01b0 vietnam hackintosh tool) l\u1ea5y m\u00e3 d\u1ef1ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1eddi macos&nbsp; <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/vi.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/MacOS\"><strong>t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y<\/strong><\/a><strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>L\u01b0u \u00fd 5: \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi 1 s\u1ed1 m\u00e1y c\u00f3 dgpu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n d\u00f9ng igpu th\u00ec disable nh\u01b0 sau&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>B1: <\/strong>Add \u0111o\u1ea1n code sau v\u00e0o boot-arg -wegnoigpu<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>B2: <\/strong>Restart v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00f4i<strong>&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>L\u01b0u \u00fd 6: C\u00f3 1 s\u1ed1 card kh\u00f4ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u1edf b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c card sau GeForce 20 series, GeForce 16 series v\u00e0 GeForce 30 series (danh s\u00e1ch c\u00e1c card h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 cho t\u1eebng card c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n xem <\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/dortania.github.io\/OpenCore-Install-Guide\/macos-limits.html#gpu-support\"><strong>t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y<\/strong><\/a><strong>)&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Ghi ch\u00fa <\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi monterey beta 9 + 1 s\u1ed1 d\u00f2ng card Geforce Kepler s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng native c\u00e1ch fix l\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd d\u00f9ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/chris1111\/Geforce-Kepler-patcher\">Geforce-Kepler-patcher<\/a> nh\u01b0 sau<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B1: c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n t\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 Geforce-Kepler-patchertheo links tr\u00ean <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B2: gi\u1ea3i n\u00e9n ra sau \u0111\u00f3 app ra desktop <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/Q2pjlzn4ZudElfXPZE8McaiJewSiuhlB6aQHkrHUkPWLQsTLfNbHGKApdY_Cmg8fDxdKhjvlrbBxg9wAa_BuCbuz-fK9rHpMNJKhRRvPL_FhWurUbplS-7gKHTju-6rKcYV2asPnnN-O8Q8PJOQFIrRR2old0CjeAZoiS11bujn8zF2N6tP7hoTLew2AvBONQ3ZB12OwkjDfNCL6Tw5wcDMDZ7txt32DsYnjX96FzDcEUCEuTB-Cysi9JaScpMtqI2XqESEVOMJc8L-yiluu_h3vIx0nYmxE8IMUfL5UDn-bkoas_DCGZad72nv2EX-crLq6rOa2LUl4JsrlN72PIqTFSlBojIj2FvFx9UEuNNRPO9yAnEkv3lswUP-mYFbtjmul3sd-IhI84hsnlhs02vr6cMXkSLkBcSmxa6z8irGfYosJDHQvbcoF0d7Vwq27MSsiXwRRBu3Sv0yaZva-oCjb_obTXN77xdPWgL0L_oaWmdG5e-B0vm-1MuBViQpdzjLH62ePUixf1cL58I6fxndd1kF58yPzZX-frOVyfoRkV0YC36uhNbgQZSfUnPKzZS72eOD5ZBxRYHL8869wbu6AqZoOYpCtpVAu7FUXXJWxPwJDIfNjVLxxZdjsfuUFcFTV7pB3dwGk9wv2Qyl0LYlkYIhuuLWlEOUz846SjJKMpg3v8Vz7TqiuHslMAU7g1kRPry81ooDBpFMkc4GOLEYT=w796-h596-no?authuser=0\" alt=\"\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>B3: c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n nh\u1ea5n run <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"https:\/\/lh3.googleusercontent.com\/d93mK3C2qT4G3dsaHv3QKCpOa9LjghtVUAScB3oxdRk8P4NoOXRhmiX8sDdEvWTIPKlMnaPC0trSHHOxovRhD7nU0VPKh2xZlbRACHDUcjaItu3KSmCd5Dcb8HYqxN3defmABN8WfgLUA4zhz5OCsaUXnnnfcA4l3yZ5lrcgH1iNiRHO8xqU1MK0JJ5HYKV_OwZ6c5U4ZyFRSpUxO56VP7Akkh